•	Tenderly Simulation API: send from, to, data, value, gas from the 0x v2 quoteResponse.transaction.*. Use the decoded trace to compute human-readable deltas and revert reasons; block execution if negative beyond slippage or if router is unverified.  ￼

Sim call (server)
const sim = await fetch('https://api.tenderly.co/api/v1/account/me/project/default/simulate', {
  method: 'POST',
  headers: { 'X-Access-Key': process.env.TENDERLY_ACCESS_KEY!, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    save: false,
    simulation_type: 'quick',
    network_id: String(chainId),
    from: intent.takerAddress,
    to: quote.quoteResponse.transaction.to,
    input: quote.quoteResponse.transaction.data,
    gas: quote.quoteResponse.transaction.gas,
    value: quote.quoteResponse.transaction.value,
  })
});
const simJson = await sim.json();
•	Gas suggestions: fetch Blocknative Gas Price API (P50/P95) for the chain and annotate the preview